=== Creation Myth ===
{{See also|Miyako Island#Myths}}
After Miyako Island was formed, the deities '''Koi-tsuno''' and '''Koitama''' descended from the heavens to Harimizu, accompanied by many other gods. After creating humans and all things on earth, they returned to the heavens. It is said that by establishing the Utaki and continuing worship, the island prospered and flourished<ref name="minwa">[http://www.pref.okinawa.jp/chiiki_ritou/simajima/minwa.html#15 The Story of the Islands: Miyako Island's Beginning] Okinawa Prefectural Government</ref><ref>Imabayashi (2015)</ref>.

